          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-blue-100 animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-200">
            Plan meals, generate AI recipes, track nutrition, and achieve your health goals with ease.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-400">
